=Joy of Life Special Edition=

2
00:01:40,123 --> 00:01:43,043
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,200
Look!

4
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:51,280
It can move.

5
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,519
If cut open, it'll bleed.

6
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:57,799
I'm growing up recently,

7
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,159
so I eat a lot every day.

8
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,159
Vegetables are good for health,

9
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,560
but I still love to eat meat.

10
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,000
Eating too much meat,

11
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,719
my nose will bleed,

12
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,599
and my nails will grow fast,

13
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:07,079
so I often have to cut them every day.

14
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,759
What nonsense are you talking about?

15
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,400
I'm telling you that I am a man.

16
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,039
Not a chess piece.

17
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,520
Not a chip.

18
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:17,039
I am a living man.

19
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,639
Why would I

20
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,719
use my life

21
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,759
to trade for a firm?

22
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,039
Xian'er, you have to understand.

23
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:29,080
If you control Neiku,

24
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,879
you're in control of

25
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,800
uncounted wealth.

26
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:36,719
Were you with my mom

27
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,960
for her money?

28
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:38,919
How dare you!

29
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,840
I can't marry her.

30
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,599
I want to live

31
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,280
for myself.

32
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:44,159
Fan Xian! Fan Xian!

33
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,360
Fan Xian.

34
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,319
Are you asleep?

35
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,360
It's Fan Sizhe.

36
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,120
I need to talk to you.

37
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,639
I'm coming in.

38
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,120
Sleeping already?

39
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:01,639
Wake up!

40
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,520
Don't sleep!

41
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:05,800
I have something to tell you.

42
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,439
How come you sleep like a log?

43
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:11,080
Fan Xian! Wake up!

44
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:13,840
Fan Xian.

45
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:15,759
haven't you slept in Danzhou?

46
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,319
Are you awake?

47
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,160
I have something to tell you.

48
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,040
Well, today,

49
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,279
I almost beat you.

50
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:42,399
It's my fault.

51
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,000
After all, we are relatives,

52
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,480
right?

53
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,519
How about this?

54
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,360
I'll book a table in a restaurant

55
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,040
at noon tomorrow.

56
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,480
Take it as my apology for you.

57
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:51,319
Is that OK?

58
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:56,319
Well, I'll take that as a “Yes”.

59
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,920
At noon tomorrow. Don't forget!

60
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:00,759
I'm leaving.

61
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,160
I'll leave this on your desk.

62
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,560
Fan Xian.

63
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:55,319
Who is he?

64
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,720
What's this?

65
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,279
He's the guard who escorted me to the capital city.

66
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,759
Why are you here?

67
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,199
There's one more thing.

68
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:09,560
Dad

69
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:10,879
