101
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,920
Why would the Investigator's Office

102
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,120
hire a criminal

103
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,600
like you?

104
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:56,120
