105
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:58,720
To pick up your former career?

106
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,199
Do you have the token for
Director-General of the Investigator's Office?

107
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:05,000
Yes, I have.

108
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,600
You will go to the Investigator's Office.

109
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,439
Maybe!

110
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,800
What are you doing?

111
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,160
The Investigator's Office has special records

112
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,800
of all cases.

113
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,560
If you can bring me

114
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,879
my file which doesn't have much importance,

115
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,800
I'd give my life

116
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,399
to you.

117
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,759
I don't want to do that.

118
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,680
I will never

119
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,519
kneel in front of you

120
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:31,399
if I have another choice.

121
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:32,279
I understand.

122
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,480
that file is nothing confidential.

123
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,559
Since you're the Director-General,

124
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,039
it's a piece of cake for you to take it out

125
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:37,840
without any trouble.

126
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,960
I'm saying it once again.

127
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:50,840
I don't want to do that.

128
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,759
I will help you

129
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,799
with one extra condition.

130
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,000
You must tell me

131
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,080
what's on the file,

132
00:09:19,799 --> 00:09:20,480
You must tell me

133
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,360
assassinate the officials

134
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,480
from the imperial court,

135
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:25,879
You must tell me

136
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,960
do you give up everything?

137
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,559
I was...

138
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:38,879
These people are...

139
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,000
The story was a cliche!

140
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,759
This common couple poured water on the street

141
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,159
and stained the royalty's dresses.

142
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,879
As a consequence, they got beaten up.

143
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:58,440
Thank you for saving my life.

144
00:09:58,919 --> 00:09:59,759
Thank you!

145
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,519
Thank you for saving my life.

146
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:04,720
The master of those people

147
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,279
is called Guo Baokun.

148
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,240
And his father is Guo Youzhi,

149
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,240
the current Minister

150
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,519
of the Board of Rites.

151
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:13,960
He has paramount power.

152
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,519
What happened next?

153
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,000
One day later,

154
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,120
I was on the wanted list of the Ministry of Penalty.

155
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,840
It's nothing but a fight.

156
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,200
Why put you on the list?

157
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,000
The charge was assassinating important officials.

158
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,279
How did they declare you guilty without evidence?

159
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:32,600
There were witnesses.

160
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:34,679
The Guos?

161
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,320
It was that couple.

162
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:47,240
I was just convicted like that

163
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:49,000
with extermination of all my family members.

164
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,159
Your family got involved as well?

165
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:54,080
My wife just got pregnant at the time.

166
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:57,360
Who saved you?

167
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:58,679
The Investigator's Office.

168
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,559
They transferred me away from the jail

169
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,480
and took away all the files

170
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,879
with just one condition.

171
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:08,240
They wanted me

172
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,279
to serve them in the Investigator's Office.

173
00:11:09,759 --> 00:11:10,399
If I agree,

174
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:11,679
they would save my family.

175
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,840
They must be attracted by your capabilities.

176
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,080
What if I don't know any Kung Fu?

177
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:18,320
Will there be vegetation

178
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,559
all over my cemetery?

179
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,120
You hate them.

180
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:24,639
Whom?

181
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,159
I mean that couple

182
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,120
After I came under the Investigator's Office,

183
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,879
I talked to them in private.

184
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:32,879
Please give me some money.

185
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,759
Please help me with some food.

186
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,879
It's very tiring, isn't it?

187
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,279
You're sweating.

188
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:41,200
Miss, please give me some food.

189
00:11:41,519 --> 00:11:42,039
Miss!

190
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,320
What a miserable boy!

191
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,360
Please give me some food! Sir!

192
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,120
Please give me some money! Sir!

193
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,799
Give some to him.

194
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,039
Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!

195
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:52,440
Not at all.

196
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:54,360
Let's go!

197
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,360
Thank you! Thank you!

198
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,480
Life is not easy for anyone.

199
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:00,200
Yeah!

200
00:12:02,759 --> 00:12:04,000
Please give me some money. Sir!

201
00:12:05,639 --> 00:12:06,600
Please help me with some food.

202
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,559
Please have mercy! Sir!

203
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:10,480
Please!

204
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,720
Please give me some money! Sir!

205
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,799
Please help me with some food.

206
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:18,720
Have mercy on me please!

207
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:21,200
Miss, please give me some food.

208
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:22,799
Have mercy on me please!

209
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:24,360
Anyone please help me?

210
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,279
Thank you! Thank you! Sir!

211
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,120
Thank you!

212
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:27,840
Thank you!

213
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:31,200
They are merely common people.

214
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,799
What can they do when they are summoned by

215
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,919
the Minister's Residence as witnesses?

216
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:44,320
Ever since then,

217
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,279
I understand that there is no black and white in this world

218
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:52,519
but just rich and poor.

219
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,240
I realized

220
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,399
I had to take my wife and children away

221
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,440
from the capital city

222
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:00,639
and spent the rest of the life

223
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:01,799
in obscurity.

224
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:05,080
So you used me for a fake death

225
00:13:05,919 --> 00:13:07,000
to run away from the Investigator's Office?

226
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,279
I went home once.

227
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,519
It's all empty now.

228
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:13,879
My family are all missing.

229
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:15,200
I am a dead man

230
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,000
in name.

231
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,039
I can't investigate it.

232
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,480
You're the only man

233
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,919
that I can trust.

234
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,559
There must be record

235
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:27,039
about my family's whereabouts.

236
00:13:28,039 --> 00:13:29,559
You have my life

237
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,360
if you can help me find them.

238
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:33,080
I don't need your life,

239
00:13:34,759 --> 00:13:35,679
but I'll help you.

240
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:09,000
My Lady, it's time to take the medicine.

241
00:14:33,879 --> 00:14:34,720
Wan'er, Wan'er,

242
00:14:34,879 --> 00:14:36,480
I'm treating you with drumsticks today.

243
00:14:37,559 --> 00:14:38,879
My Lady! My Lady!

244
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,080
Watch out for the wind!

245
00:14:41,879 --> 00:14:42,480
Miss!

246
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:52,559
Lady Ye,

247
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:53,639
what new idea

248
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:54,440
do you have today?

249
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,360
I went out of town yesterday
to watch sword shows on the street

250
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,440
and learned that a chef

251
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,919
can make dishes out of grains, vegetables, and beans

252
00:15:00,919 --> 00:15:02,360
with the taste of various meats

253
00:15:02,879 --> 00:15:03,759
which is not only tasty

254
00:15:03,879 --> 00:15:04,840
but also vivid.

255
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,320
So I brought him here

256
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,240
to satisfy your craving for food.

257
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,879
You're so considerate.

258
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,279
Of course!

259
00:15:12,919 --> 00:15:13,519
If you have a craving for any food

260
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,600
in future,

261
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:17,320
I'll bring him to you.

262
00:15:20,879 --> 00:15:22,759
I have no luck to enjoy them

263
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,960
despite how honored I am.

264
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,720
Are you alright?

265
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:32,399
You are spitting blood again.

266
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,840
Did you catch a cold yesterday

267
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:35,559
when visiting the Qing Temple?

268
00:15:38,039 --> 00:15:38,600
I'm fine!

269
00:15:40,279 --> 00:15:41,120
Totally fine.

270
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,200
Do you think

271
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:49,679
some day

272
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:52,600
I would get used to

273
00:15:53,399 --> 00:15:54,360
spitting blood.

274
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,679
No way!

275
00:15:59,559 --> 00:16:00,600
I'll find a famous reclused doctor for you

276
00:16:01,279 --> 00:16:02,840
some day when I go out of town.

277
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,600
You'll be cured.

278
00:16:07,279 --> 00:16:08,440
In view of the current situation,

279
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,080
I won't be happy

280
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,600
even if I'm cured.

281
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,639
You're still concerned about the bestowed marriage?

282
00:16:17,039 --> 00:16:17,919
I know the situation

283
00:16:17,919 --> 00:16:19,200
about my body.

284
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:21,120
I could die any time.

285
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:23,200
Why would I die with the marriage contract?

286
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:24,679
That's bullshit!

287
00:16:26,879 --> 00:16:28,240
You don't have to blame yourself

288
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,120
for a bastard.

289
00:16:31,159 --> 00:16:32,159
He is a bastard.

290
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,720
So am I.

291
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,919
What's the difference?

