00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,640
I'm willing to pay ten times as much

458
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,359
for the map.

459
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:24,640
That's delightful!

460
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:25,839
I always have the courage

461
00:23:26,359 --> 00:23:28,000
